  ~     - https://github.com/aosp-mirror/platform_frameworks_support/blob/master/v7/appcompat/res/layout/select_dialog_item_material.xml
  ~ Ref:
  ~     - https://material.io/guidelines/components/dialogs.html#dialogs-specs
